    <h3>Coloureyes</h3>
    <p>
      As far as Web dev is concerned, I've published two sites on Heroku.
      The first was a basic local storage colour picker application called 
      'Coloureyes', with which you can save colours as favourites and also 
      group them into palettes (handy if you're designing something). The code 
